{"tid":842731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奸夫淫婦叫Uber離開酒店 咁啱就係老公做司機","createTime":"2018-09-30T14:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T14:54:20.000Z","uid":41343,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"115e8833ee1bae94be074b494eaf02df0327cc6d","tid":842731,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"有些事情冥冥中自有主宰，哥倫比亞一位人妻趁丈夫工作時約上情夫赴酒店開房，事後叫Uber車離開，沒料到接單的就是自己丈夫，令不忠關係曝光。<br />\n<br />\n耶米（Yeimi）周二與情夫在聖瑪爾塔（Santa Marta）一間酒店幽會後叫車離開，接單的司機名叫里安納度（Leonardo），她們見司機並非自己認識的人就確認服務。<br />\n<br />\n然而抵達的碰巧是耶米的丈夫，原來他是里安納度的朋友，當時是代友接單。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道耶米與情夫見狀拔腿就跑，不過被丈夫抓住，當場質問她與情夫的關係。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180930/58740100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58740100&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8jey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=813066a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58740100&h=25dee935\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180930/58740100</a>"},{"pid":"d20c9acf2af7bd8ad61ca856a60949faad48a2f4","tid":842731,"uid":149566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"tvb劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e87923ddd556796aba6472f337aeba5d6c8c6cc","tid":842731,"uid":132587,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/fantendo/images/0/09/Luigi_Artwork_%28alt%29_-_Mario_Kart_8.png/revision/latest?cb=20140316111009\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Ffantendo%2Fimages%2F0%2F09%2FLuigi_Artwork_%2528alt%2529_-_Mario_